{"tid":1031009,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「學習強國」APP 下載量超微信  但街訪沒人聽過 市民：「花錢買流量、買排名吧」","createTime":"2019-02-21T11:09:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-21T11:48:26.000Z","uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"47a365b5b926ffac2bd009d7274753144fb562e1","tid":1031009,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T11:09:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/243749166571823/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F243749166571823%2F&d=YG7PnvT15JjBub1A77CHD3PcKSbPy461JM9tWmz6mNY%3D&h=8814a8f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/243749166571823/</a><br />\n<br />\n【「學習強國」APP 下載量超微信】<br />\n【但街訪沒人聽過】<br />\n【市民：「花錢買流量、買排名吧」】<br />\n<br />\n內地近期最熱門的應用程式，不是抖音也不是微信，而是推廣中共總書記習近平思想的「學習強國」App，上至公務員、國企員工到非黨員人士都被要求下載學習。<br />\n<br />\n除了看習近平新聞，「學習強國」App亦是一個社交平台，用家可以邀請朋友聊天、進行視頻會議，要「交流學習心得」也很方便。該APP至今已被下載超過4千萬次，是否真的那麼受歡迎？<br />\n<br />\n駐廣州記者在街上問了半個小時，只有一個人聽過，那4千多萬的下載量是怎麼來的呢？<br />\n<br />\n市民李先生說：「應該是花了錢買流量、買排名吧，不然的話正常來說，我看我身邊的同事，好像沒有人下載，但是我知道這個排名第一。」<br />\n<br />\n現實世界找不到有下載的人，我們就看看網上世界怎麼看。有人說每日使用「學習強國」已經是習慣，不過亦有人批評，「學習強國」接受不了批評和反對聲音，一旦發表負面言論就會被刪除。<br />\n<br />\n路透社引述阿里巴巴員工指，這個APP是公司旗下一個不為人知的特別專案團隊開發，而這個團隊專門承擔公司以外的業務。<br />\n<br />\n有人就反映下載學習強國後，會自動以阿里旗下的一款社交軟件登陸，擔心聊天記錄同資料，都會被學習強國APP使用，質疑阿里巴巴已經成為「新國企」。<br />\n<br />\n#學習強國<br />\n#宇宙最強<br />\n#習近平<br />\n#有線中國組"},{"pid":"01b80d2f4fd8d0b4fa7f054e12b5998e1deb672b","tid":1031009,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T11:32:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2270000/2274247/3_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2270000%2F2274247%2F3_1024.jpg&h=8c540507&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"acbd478d1d74bb3bdf6abd6adbd5233b3e37ae12","tid":1031009,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T11:35:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/techstart.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/螢幕快照-2019-02-19-下午4.57.06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2F%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E5%BF%AB%E7%85%A7-2019-02-19-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%884.57.06.jpg&h=fa93b7f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hsygsyxx.com/manage/kindeditor/attached/image/20190131/20190131201351775177.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhsygsyxx.com%2Fmanage%2Fkindeditor%2Fattached%2Fimage%2F20190131%2F20190131201351775177.jpg&h=99222caf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a23a2ebe757c88de949eb8d207bafc185a9373c","tid":1031009,"uid":170772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T11:48:26.000Z","msg":"已經走火入魔"}]}